==========================================
Description of the files in this directory
==========================================

risc8doc.html : This files is provided by the developer of the DUT code and
		used as it is. It expains the details of the risc8 architecture
		and specification.

NOTE : We have changed the expansion circuit block with the traffic light 
       controller block to show more functionality with VCS. Other files
       in dut/ directory are used as it is, provided by the developer. 
